abstract: The United States Justice Department is looking into Google’s takeover of airline ticketing software firm ITA Software, to determine whether the deal would exert too much influence on the online travel industry, Reuters said, citing a report in The Wall Street Journal.

lead_paragraph: The United States Justice Department is looking into Google‘s takeover of airline ticketing software firm ITA Software, to determine whether the deal would exert too much influence on the online travel industry, Reuters said, citing a report in The Wall Street Journal.

headline.main: Justice Department Probes Google ITA Deal
